</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">10亿个整数（去重判断）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  HashSet: 10亿 * 4字节 ≈ 4GB（不考虑HashMap开销）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  位图: 10亿 bit = 10^9 / 8 ≈ 119MB
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  压缩比: 4GB / 119MB ≈ 34倍</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
